---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

export const prerender = true;
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="FTC-compliant affiliate disclosure for OpenClaw Alt."
  canonicalUrl="https://openclawalts.com/disclosure"
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-14 sm:py-20">

    <h1 style="font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 900; color: #f1f5f9; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>

    <p class="text-sm mb-8" style="color: #475569;">Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none
      prose-headings:font-['Fraunces']
      prose-a:text-[#00d4aa]
      prose-strong:text-white
      prose-hr:border-white/10"
      style="color: #cbd5e1;">

      <p>
        OpenClaw Alt (<strong>openclawalts.com</strong>) participates in affiliate marketing programs. This means we may earn a commission when you click a link on this site and make a purchase — at <strong>no additional cost to you</strong>.
      </p>

      <h2>FTC Compliance</h2>

      <p>
        In accordance with the Federal Trade Commission (FTC) guidelines concerning the use of endorsements and testimonials in advertising (<a href="https://www.ftc.gov/tips-advice/business-center/guidance/ftcs-endorsement-guides-what-people-are-asking" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">16 CFR Part 255</a>), we disclose that some links on this site are affiliate links.
      </p>

      <h2>What this means for you</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Clicking an affiliate link will take you to a third-party website.</li>
        <li>If you purchase a product or sign up for a service through that link, we may receive compensation.</li>
        <li>The price you pay is <strong>not affected</strong> by whether you use our affiliate link or navigate to the site directly.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our editorial independence</h2>

      <p>
        Affiliate relationships do not influence our editorial content. We review and recommend tools based on our honest assessment of their value. We do not write positive reviews in exchange for compensation, and we clearly note drawbacks and limitations alongside any advantages.
      </p>

      <p>
        We only link to products and services we believe provide genuine value. If we wouldn't use a tool ourselves, we won't recommend it.
      </p>

      <h2>Current affiliate relationships</h2>

      <p>
        At the time of publication, we have or may have affiliate relationships with the following companies mentioned on this site:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>n8n</strong> — 30% recurring commission for 12 months</li>
        <li><strong>Lindy</strong> — 30% first year, 15% second year</li>
        <li><strong>GetDynamIQ</strong> — 50% for 12 months</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        This list may be updated as we add new content and affiliate relationships.
      </p>

      <h2>Questions?</h2>

      <p>
        If you have questions about our affiliate relationships or editorial practices, see our <a href="/about">About page</a>.
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
